tions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Patrickpoix/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Patrickpoix/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Patrickpoix/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Patrickpoix/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Patrickpoix/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2026-07-10T21:02:55Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T21:02:55Z","closed_at":null,"assignee":null,"author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"## 中文说明\n\n### 问题摘要\nCodex++ 1.2.34 将 Chat Completions 响应转换为 Responses API 时，为 assistant message item 生成 `resp_<response-id>_msg`。当切换到官方 OpenAI provider 并重放历史时，官方接口拒绝请求：\n\n```text\n[ApiIdParam] [input[6].id] [invalid_id_prefix]\nInvalid input id: resp_..._msg. Expected an ID that begins with msg_.\n```\n\n结果是：第三方 relay 创建的历史会话在 Provider Sync 后仍然可见，但无法在官方 provider 下继续。\n\n### 环境\n- Windows 11\n- Codex++ 1.2.34\n- Codex session metadata: 0.144.0-alpha.4\n- Chat Completions upstream converted to Responses\n\n### 复现步骤\n1. 配置 `chatCompletions` relay。\n2. 创建会话并收到 assistant 回复。\n3. rollout 中 message `response_item.id` 为 `resp_..._msg`。\n4. 切换或同步到官方 `openai` provider。\n5. 续接同一会话。\n6. 官方 Responses API 返回 `invalid_id_prefix`。\n\n### 源码定位\n非流式转换：\nhttps://github.com/BigPizzaV3/CodexPlusPlus/blob/v1.2.34/crates/codex-plus-core/src/protocol_proxy.rs#L2869-L2917\n\n```rust\n\"id\": format!(\"{response_id}_msg\"),\n```\n\n流式 SSE 转换：\nhttps://github.com/BigPizzaV3/CodexPlusPlus/blob/v1.2.34/crates/codex-plus-core/src/protocol_proxy.rs#L1250-L1270\n\n```rust\nlet item_id = format!(\"{}_msg\", self.response_id);\n```\n\n`response_id` 本身以 `resp_` 开头：\nhttps://github.com/BigPizzaV3/CodexPlusPlus/blob/v1.2.34/crates/codex-plus-core/src/protocol_proxy.rs#L942-L949\n\n因此 message item ID 会成为 `resp_*_msg`。\n\n### 预期行为\nassistant message item ID 应以 `msg_` 开头，流式和非流式路径应使用同一规范。\n\n### 建议修复\n1. 增加统一的 message item ID 生成函数。\n2. 生成 `msg_<stable-unique-suffix>`，不要在 `resp_*` 后追加 `_msg`。\n3. 同时修复流式与非流式转换。\n4. 添加回归测试，断言所有 `type: message` output item ID 均以 `msg_` 开头。\n5. 为已持久化 `resp_*_msg` 的 rollout 增加兼容迁移或重放清理逻辑。\n\n## English summary\nCodex++ 1.2.34 generates assistant message item IDs as `{response_id}_msg` in both streaming and non-streaming Chat Completions-to-Responses conversion. Since the response ID begins with `resp_`, persisted rollout items get IDs like `resp_*_msg`.\n\nWhen resumed through the official OpenAI provider, the Responses API rejects the replayed item with `invalid_id_prefix`, because message item IDs must begin with `msg_`.\n\nPlease generate spec-compatible `msg_*` IDs in both paths, add regression coverage, and consider compatibility handling for already persisted rollout histories.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/BigPizzaV3/CodexPlusPlus/issues/1431/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/BigPizzaV3/CodexPlusPlus/issues/1431/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null,"pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/BigPizzaV3/CodexPlusPlus/issues/459","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/BigPizzaV3/CodexPlusPlus","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/BigPizzaV3/CodexPlusPlus/issues/459/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/BigPizzaV3/CodexPlusPlus/issues/459/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/BigPizzaV3/CodexPlusPlus/issues/459/events","html_url":"https://github.com/BigPizzaV3/CodexPlusPlus/issues/459","id":4557119359,"node_id":"I_kwDOSVvFfs8AAAABD6Affw","number":459,"title":"[Bug]:","user":{"logi